        <p>
            With the goal of accellerating MRR growth, we needed an outbound strategy targeting a lucrative segment. My sales counterpart saw potential in the contact center space because productivity a top priority and many viewed remote work as permanent. I took the insight and created a customer acquisition strategy. The plan was executed by myself and two creative professionals. We achieved these results over the course of a year.    
        </p>
