            </li>
            <li>
                Increased average deal size and grew sales pipeline to record highs.  
            </li>
            <li>
                Acquired a dozen new contact center customers while maintaining inbound channels. 
            </li>
        </ul>
        <p>
            Most leads generated by the effort are still active. With time more contact center customers are expected to convert and generate return on investment higher than the breakeven level at the end of this case study.  
